            <title>[FLINK-6690] Rescaling broken</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-6690</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Rescaling appears to be broken for both 1.3 and 1.4. WHen i tried it out i got the following exception:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
